      • defaultTemplate

        public static RepresentationTemplateDefinition defaultTemplate(java.lang.String entityName,
                                                               java.util.Collection<java.lang.String> attributeIdentifiers)
        Create a new default representation template model for the given entity name and attribute identifiers.

        The default representation template for the entity "edge" with the attributes ["from", "to"] is: edge(::from,::to)

        Parameters:
        entityName - entity name which is used to generate the default representation template
        attributeIdentifiers - attribute identifiers which is used to generate the default representation template
        Returns:
        model instance
